\f0\fs28 \cf2 it is about preserving the intellectual integrity of information objects, including capturing information about the various contexts within which information is created, organized, and used; organic relationships with other information objects; and characteristics that provide meaning and evidential value (Gilliland-Swetland, 2000, p.29).}

{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg1252\cocoartf1265\cocoasubrtf190
