\f0\fs28 \cf2 or digital materials \'91their preservation must be an integral element of the initial design of systems and projects\'92 (Ross, 2000, p.13), but this is not usually the case. Digital materials exist in a bewilderingly large number of formats; there is still little standardization. The most significant concept is that the preservation of digital materials is much more than the preservation of information content or physical carrier}

