\f0\fs28 \cf2 \'93A cash withdrawal has an account, an account owner, an amount, a date, and a bank. A report has an author, a title, an intended audience, and a defined subject and scope. A contract has provisions, contracting parties, and an effective date.\'94 (Thibodeau 2002 p9)}

