\f0\fs28 \cf2 \'93Determining which functions, work processes, activities, or individuals are likely to produce records of enduring value and which are not \'96 rather than reading directly (in larger jurisdictions) billions of records or tens of thousands of series to try to gauge their potential historical research values.\'94}

